title: Title Track Lyrics Tik Tik Tik
stanzas:
Tik Tik Tik Title Track Lyrics from Tik Tik Tik 

Un sevigalil
chottu chottena
kaalath thuliyaa ? 

ivvadhirvugal 
undhan irudhayam
kottum oliyaa?

evvaththin udhikaana
nee aatrum yedhum
evvaaru inge pizhai?

avvaththin thulimondu
..
avvaanil engae mazhai

vidhi siridhu
madhi peridhu
thadai siridhu
vidai peridhu

vali sirudhu
vazhi peridhu
porul siridhu
arul peridhu

tik tik tik ..

chottu chottena
kaalath thuliyaa?

sarindhu vittaa podhum
kuzhandhaigal pol nirkka
pidivadham vendum

iravu vaanathai paar
jolikkum natchathiram
angae naam pogalaam vaa
erikulaa ....

kanavugal nijamaagalaam
dhinamum munnetram adainthaal
naatilirundhu vinvelikku
...

oadi oadi naadi thaedi
ilakku adaivadhu latchiyam
vettriyodu naam thirumbuvomey
uyarvin saththiyam

namakkena pala porgal
irukkaiyil
veliyil irundhu oru
vinkal varuvadhaa

adhai udaithidu
kadhavadaithidu
pinnaam poriduvom

mozhi madha inam
pedham irukkaiyil.
nammai azhithida
vaanam vizhuvadhaa

adhai thaduthidu
kadhai mudithidu
pinne naam azhivom

nurai siridhu
karai peridhu
thadam siridhu
idam peridhu

vizhum manadhu
ezhum pozhudhu
thuyar siridhu
uyir peridhu

aattralin ellaigal
udaithu meeruvom

anjaadha ullangal
ondraaga koodinaal
marana pidiyai
thaamadham aakkuvom

kedigaram naadi thudikkum
tik tik tik
nodiyinai pol
oli vedikkum 
tik tik tik 

avasarathil kadhai 
mudippom 
tik tik tik 

coz you know 
when  we do it
we do it quick and slick

nammudan payirichi
thiranin valarchi
manidhanin pudhi
can conquer gravity!!
nammul vazhum sakthi
more than technology
kaatume than nambikkai
vettrik kaana sannadhi

tik tik tik !!
